'''2016年基里巴斯總統選舉'''于2016年3月9日举行，反對黨[[关爱基里巴斯党|关爱基里巴斯党]]候選人[[塔內希·馬茂|塔內希·馬茂]]取得近六成選票，擊敗屬{{le|聯合同盟黨|United Coalition Party}}、由執政黨[[追求真理党|追求真理党]]提名的{{le|瑞米塔·拜尼阿米纳|Rimeta Beniamina}}當選<ref>[http://www.radionz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/298579/taneti-maamau-declared-new-president-of-kiribati Taneti Maamau declared new president of Kiribati] {{Wayback|url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/298579/taneti-maamau-declared-new-president-of-kiribati |date=20160313103613 }} Radio New Zealand, 10 March 2016</ref><ref>[http://www.trtworld.com/asia/maamau-becomes-kiribati-president-64877 Maamau becomes Kiribati president] {{Wayback|url=http://www.trtworld.com/asia/maamau-becomes-kiribati-president-64877 |date=20160311192902 }} TRT World, 10 March 2016</ref>。

